name: Skydiving Frenzy!
description:
INSTRUCTIONS:

  • Left and Right Arrows/ A and D to Move
  • Avoid the other Skydivers
  • Get the High Score!

MODES:

  • Normal - Classic Skydiving Frenzy!
  • Moving - The other Skydivers move (and go a little faster)!
  • Target - The other Skydivers will always come straight at you; be ready!
  • Free - The other Skydivers come from all angles!

Thanks for playing :D
